{"tid":2180417,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–皮膚傷口不留疤痕的研究","createTime":"2020-08-29T22:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T17:41:51.000Z","uid":38861,"like":77,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"f7374094e67d172353d70cbf1c52e8c813764c6f","tid":2180417,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T22:03:03.000Z","msg":"皮膚受傷的時候，大多數的情況下都會出現結焦情況，過一段時間後傷口便會縫合。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AndBtGG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAndBtGG.jpg&h=be640330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時候，皮膚會留有疤痕，但又有一些情況下會不留痕跡般似的進行修復，就像沒有事發生過一樣。<br />\n<br />\n究竟最終會否留有疤痕，是看幸運還是甚麼呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）近日，有科學家發表文章(Ref1)，對此作出了一個頗為完滿的解答。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RHOt4e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRHOt4e6.jpg&h=4c174c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他們在老鼠耳仔上開一個細洞，然後再緊密觀察其康復情況。他們發現塗上會引起發炎作用的Imiquimod(IMQ)後，傷口會完美修復不留疤。<br />\n<br />\n而在缺乏TRPA1神經細胞的老鼠，就算塗上(IMQ)，傷口始終會留有疤痕，表示TRPA1神經細胞在皮膚的修復上顯然有著重要作用。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）他們進行了一系列的實驗，最終找出了箇中機制，以下為最簡化版本。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdQ8jOw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdQ8jOw.jpg&h=3f44d23e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.傷口塗上IMQ後，將會引起發炎作用。<br />\n2.發炎作用刺激TRPA1神經細胞。<br />\n3.免疫系統細胞（dermal dendritic cells、&gamma;&delta; T cells）被傳召前來。<br />\n4.免疫系統細胞釋出相關物質（Interlunkin17、22、23）。<br />\n5.一系列的過程發生過後，肌膚完美修復。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此研究的結果針對於老鼠的皮膚癒合情況，未必能套用在人類身上，需要作出人體試驗才能廣泛證實此結果。<br />\n另外，IMQ的塗用時機還需要進一步確認，何時觸發發炎作用才是適當的時機還需要一系列的測試。<br />\n<br />\n不過有一點非常重要的是，當人類皮膚受傷的時候，自身是不會主動觸動TRPA1神經細胞。<br />\n若然整個結果能套用在人類身上的話，那亦是代表我們日後可塗上適當的藥膏刺激皮膚下的TRPA1細胞，觸發一系列的過程使傷口以不留疤痕的方式完美癒合！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLDHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=16425c23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLDHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=52461d5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n最後亦請幫一幫忙簽署袁爸的白宮呈請，幫忙為香港出一份力。<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/support-hong-kong-restart-clean-2020-legislative-council-election-now\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsupport-hong-kong-restart-clean-2020-legislative-council-election-now&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLDHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=dc6b854e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/support-hong-kong-restart-clean-2020-legislative-council-election-now</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://immunology.sciencemag.org/content/5/50/eaba5683\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimmunology.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F5%2F50%2Feaba5683&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLDHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=15e34343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://immunology.sciencemag.org/content/5/50/eaba5683</a>"},{"pid":"96dedcb67ad22a109e6b5feceaaf0a839a96fbb6","tid":2180417,"uid":146055,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T22:06:25.000Z","msg":"每日一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3eb730db7ba5617ab93ea22e6365143404a5a3","tid":2180417,"uid":38861,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96dedcb67ad22a109e6b5feceaaf0a839a96fbb6","tid":2180417,"uid":146055,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T22:06:25.000Z","msg":"每日一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T22:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每日為大家帶來最新/有趣的科學資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e89b7b1781568e338595acf3a4ce7860084495","tid":2180417,"uid":93385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T22:13:20.000Z","msg":"咁有咩藥膏係可以刺激皮膚下嘅TRPA1細胞？"},{"pid":"eab84aa992bba4a4dd5ee7a48528dfdd490ebe71","tid":2180417,"uid":342854,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T22:15:11.000Z","msg":"支持 失眠望電話睇到 幫推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"206cbbdd6d47dcf77c0d069ca1d79292292f5413","tid":2180417,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12e89b7b1781568e338595acf3a4ce7860084495","tid":2180417,"uid":93385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T22:13:20.000Z","msg":"咁有咩藥膏係可以刺激皮膚下嘅TRPA1細胞？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T22:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都未證實依套方法啱唔啱人類使用，唔好亂試<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24726d487d8e17d7aec866f07a11598292c97842","tid":2180417,"uid":323855,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,